# ORBit ZMK-Conf — track firmware config + docs only.
# CAD/binary artifacts (STL/3MF), build scripts, and scratch folders
# stay LOCAL. They remain on disk and in git history; they're just not
# tracked going forward.

# Ignore everything at the top level by default...
/*

# ...except the firmware config, docs, and CI we deliberately track:
!/.gitignore
!/.github/
!/README.md
!/FIRMWARE_SPEC.md
!/HARDWARE_VALIDATION.md
!/zmk-config/

# Never track OS cruft or editor swap files, at any depth.
.DS_Store
*.kate-swp
*.swp
